{"tid":2201427,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"深入淺出–人工降雨","createTime":"2020-09-13T19:54:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T10:17:12.000Z","uid":38861,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"173e4e8ae594506910f22c0cac3049d58236b331","tid":2201427,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:54:10.000Z","msg":"近兩日看到了下面一則新聞，因而生起念頭寫上本篇文章，介紹一下人工降雨的概念。<br />\n<br />\n「中國福建省寧德市因日前缺雨，官方宣布8日至9日將進行「人工降雨」，不料，8日下午市區突降暴雨、嚴重淹水，不但汽車直接泡水中，還一度緊急撤離居民，民眾懷疑應是「人工降雨」劑量錯誤釀禍，感嘆「寧德大概是第一個因為人工降雨把自己淹掉的城市吧！」，對此，官方未多做說明。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/j77XJyx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fj77XJyx.jpg&h=79bf8135&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）要了解人工降雨的原理，我們自當然要快速了解一下雲到底是如何形成，以及甚麼條件會觸發下雨事件發生。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9302UFg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9302UFg.jpg&h=a639d437&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n太陽為大地帶來溫暖，亦同時把海洋的水份蒸發成氣體上天。<br />\n<br />\n高度越高，溫度便會越低，水蒸氣亦會變成為水珠。<br />\n而當水珠遇上各種微粒（如圖中所示）後，便能在其上凝結。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖3）凝結在微粒的水珠最終會變成為結晶狀。當這些結晶集合一起後，便會形成雲。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7AmhJyH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7AmhJyH.jpg&h=88b433a6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨著時間推進，大地的水蒸氣不斷湧上天空，源源不絕的水珠不斷在結晶上繼續凝結，導致結晶體積越來越大。<br />\n<br />\n當結晶體積大到某一個程度的時候，便會因著地心吸力的緣故降落到地上，亦即是雨。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖4）其中一種人工降雨的方式，亦是中國在北京奧運及西藏地區常用的手段，就是利用地上燃燒或者飛機、無人機以及火箭的方式把化學物（silver iodide,AgI）注入到雲中裡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2Lujcr5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2Lujcr5.jpg&h=1f0b2df0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nAgI的角色就是促進水珠結晶的形成，提供一個優越的表面讓雨裡的水珠凝結，加速結晶體積增加的速度，最終誘使雨水降到地上。<br />\n<br />\n這種人工的方式至少有兩種限制，一就是雲隻的存在，若果天上沒有雲的話，你送多少AgI上天也是徒勞無功的。<br />\n<br />\n二就是雲隻的溫度，雲的溫度隨著高度亦會有所不同，只有低過攝氏零度的雲隻AgI才會發揮顯著功效(Ref1,2)。<br />\n<br />\n因此，這種人工降雨的方式必需配合各種的天氣感測或量度系統輔助，才能找出適當的時機製造人工降雨。<br />\n<br />\n另一方面，這種人工降雨的方式無疑是先洗未來錢，中國在2018年的西藏地區至少興建了500個焚化爐（Ref3)，意圖大幅增加西藏地區的降雨量。<br />\n<br />\n這種手段間接促使到鄰近地區無法獲取充足雨水，這責任又應該是由誰來負責呢？而且，瘋狂運送科學物到天空，受害的最終會是誰?<br />\n<br />\n那些「不應存在天上」的化學物，又是否會導致酸雨發生呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去<span class=\"blue\">Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單</span>俾一個<span class=\"green\">like</span>以及<span class=\"red\">Bookmark</span>，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8FDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=303be920\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「<span class=\"gold\">買一嚿/半嚿薯仔</span>」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8FDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=743fa859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有興趣接收科學資訊的話，歡迎follow IG: potatopigtongue。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.1716995115\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.pnas.org%2Fcgi%2Fdoi%2F10.1073%2Fpnas.1716995115&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8FDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=f9417632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.pnas.org/cgi/doi/10.1073/pnas.1716995115</a><br />\nRef2:<a href=\"https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S092188311000169X\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS092188311000169X&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8FDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=c184a970\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/abs/pii/S092188311000169X</a><br />\nRef3:<a href=\"https://singularityhub.com/2018/04/24/china-plans-to-bring-artificial-rain-to-area-three-times-the-size-of-spain/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fsingularityhub.com%2F2018%2F04%2F24%2Fchina-plans-to-bring-artificial-rain-to-area-three-times-the-size-of-spain%2F&d=L%2FLAiDqbkajbTQHtoaAw8FDApO%2Br9QW7Zx2priNtVuo%3D&h=40c13a98\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://singularityhub.com/2018/04/24/china-plans-to-bring-artificial-rain-to-area-three-times-the-size-of-spain/</a>"},{"pid":"5de9e64bcd416982c0850e2f85d95cc96a5220a2","tid":2201427,"uid":1886,"like":1,"dislike":39,"score":-38,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T19:55:53.000Z","msg":"<code>Windows Cortana 留名系統啟動，</code><br />\n<code>請勿負評干擾運作。</code>"},{"pid":"fcbe0da2728b31c3bbd8b59fa3f23139a9c806b8","tid":2201427,"uid":199244,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T20:01:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"776fd5c2d5154adfb916a105b5c05e2a1b281c03","tid":2201427,"uid":220649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T20:04:49.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2aa5f644e58574ed778e2b17014cd266f326044c","tid":2201427,"uid":38861,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"776fd5c2d5154adfb916a105b5c05e2a1b281c03","tid":2201427,"uid":220649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-13T20:04:49.000Z","msg":"巴打好有心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif